Body (Html):
About this item

Patanjali Herbal Mehandi (Henna) is made from goodness of 11 herbs
It naturally conditions and colors the hair
As a conditioner, it strengthens the hair and reduces dandruff
It improves hair growth, reduces hair fall and provides cooling to scalp
Patanjali herbal Mehandi is a product of Ayurvedic herbals like neem, amla, methi seeds
It removes dandruff and enhances the beauty, strength of the hair

Product description

Naturally condition and colour your hair to reveal its innate beauty with Patanjali Herbal Mehandi. This henna pack is enhanced with 11 herbs and enriches the hair, reduces dandruff and strengthens roots. With regular use, the pre-wash conditioner improves hair growth, softens and straightens hair and reduces hair fall. An Ayurvedic product, the cooling herbal conditioner is rich in the extracts of neem, amla and methi seeds. Mehandi�s ability to improve the texture and colour of hair has made it a conditioner of choice for centuries in India. Patanjali Herbal Mehandi stirs in the additional benefits of Ayurveda�s secrets to the mehandi recipe that has traditionally been handed from one generation to the next and gives you hair that is lustrous and dazzles with its natural silkiness. Use once a week or as often required.

Product description

Patanjali Kesh Kanti Aloe Vera Hair Cleanser is packed with the cleansing and restoring properties of Aloe vera, combined with a variety of nourishing herbs. The extracts of the Aloe plant calm affected scalps and moisturize dry and damaged hair. Title: Patanjali Kesh Kanti Dandruff Care Shampoo
Body (Html):
About this item 

This gives beauty to the hairs, treating dryness and dandruffs
Bhrigraj, myrtle (mahendi), acadia concinna (shikakai) and emblic myrobalan (aola), give new strength to the hairs. Soap nut (ritha), margosa (neem), Indian valerian (tagar), esculent fiacurtia (bakuchi) and turmeric, fights with the insecticides and are effective disinfectants, particularly in the root of hairs
Aloe vera, aola and kesh kanti stops hair loss and hair turning grey and keeps up shinning
Usage: Apply liberally to wet hair and work lather through strands, from scalp to ends. Rinse well with water. 

Product description

Kesh Kanti Anti Dandruff Shampoo gives you a deeply cleansing action that acts on the dirt contained in the scalp and reduces the dandruff to a great extent. It also leaves you with glossy and healthy looking hair thanks to its nourishing properties and elements.

Title: Patanjali Chyawanprash Plus ( Herbal Jam )
Body (Html):
About this item

    DELICIOUS SPREADABLE JAM: Patanjali Chyavanprash jam is a herbal cooked mixture and has been eaten for health, digestion, stress and energy in India for generations. Now enjoy the same historical goodness in your home. It tastes sweet and sour at the same time.
    HERBAL MIXTURE FOR ALL AGES - Patanjali Chyavanprash jam is an everyday restorative of health promoting strong body and bright mind in children and adults.
    TASTY AND HEALTHY - it has a tangy sweet-sour taste and the consistency of jam so it is delicious on toast, bread spread, mixed into warm milk, or even eaten by the spoonful directly.
    CHYAVANPRASH is a delicious Ayurvedic herbal jam that is prepared in a base of fresh amalaki (amla) fruit, a natural source of antioxidants. This nutritious jam removes physical & mental weakness caused by any reason and strengthens immune system.
    QUALITY CONTROL - All our products are carefully packaged under the most hygienic conditions according to international quality standard.


Product Description

Patanjali Chyawanprash has come into Ayurveda through the tradition of the Indian. Patanjali Chyawanprash is the best herbal formulation & not just meant for sick people but is excellent for healthy people too. Chyawanprash is a time-tested Ayurvedic formulation of more than 41 Ayurvedic herbs that aid in boosting the immune system.
